HOW TO USE

1. Paste the folder ui5-util in your webapp folder
2. You can call the relevant file in the controller :
/*
*		sap.ui.define([
*			"sap/ui/core/mvc/Controller",
*			"../ui5-util/Utilities"
*		], function (Controller, Util) {
*			"use strict";
*			return Controller.extend("ui5.util.ui5-util.controller.View", {
*				Util: util,	// For usage in XML Views
*				onInit: function () {
*					Util.method(arg);
*				}
*			});
*		});
*/

2bis. Or use it in a XML view (if it's already declared in the associated controller) :

/*
*	<Input change=".util.method(arg)"/>
*/